text: Kiran Maheshwari (29 October 1961 â€“ 30 November 2020) was an Indian politician. She was born in Udaipur, Rajasthan. Maheshwari was a member of the Bharatiya Janata Party. She was a member of the Lok Sabha from 2004 to 2009. Maheshwari died of COVID-19 on 30 November 2020 at a hospital in Gurgaon, Haryana at the age of 59.Ashok Gehlot condoles the death of BJP MLA Kiran Maheshwari ==References== Category:1961 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Gurgaon Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians Category:Rajasthani politicians Category:Members of the Lok Sabha
